Veyron Notice:

This software was not built to blend in.

It was designed, engineered, and refined with the unreasonable expectation
that software should feel less like a tool and more like an achievement.

If you are reading this license, you are looking at the result of countless
iterations, experiments, failures, and decisions made by someone who refused
to ship something ordinary.

You are free to use it, improve it, and build upon it.

Just remember where it started.

Great software is rarely created by following the crowd.

